  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/18/microsoft-app-store-developer-responses-roll-out/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/bf876e13ed62a690f64a0e8e716257a2/200046096/MicrosoftComments.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 394px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div>如果你是那种喜欢给应用留下评价的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/windowsphone\">Windows Phone</a> 用户的话，那未来哪天开发者针对你的建议给出回应时，可千万不要太惊讶。微软已于日前向开发者开放了这项功能，让他们也可以对用户的评价发布自己的意见。不过值得一提的是，微软不会把用户的个人细节提供给开发者，而且若是开发者的反应有不妥之处的话，使用者也可以向微软反映情况。这样的举措无疑将有助于应用品质的提高，当然，前提是开发者必须要能听得进意见啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/04/18/microsoft-app-store-developer-responses-roll-out/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://thenextweb.com/microsoft/2014/04/17/microsoft-launches-pilot-program-letting-windows-phone-developers-respond-app-reviews/\" target=\"_blank\">The Next Web</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://blogs.windows.com/windows_phone/b/windowsphone/archive/2014/04/17/you-may-soon-get-a-response-to-your-windows-phone-app-review.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Microsoft</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://blogs.windows.com/windows/b/buildingapps/archive/2014/04/17/respond-to-app-reviews-a-phased-rollout.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">(2)</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/18/microsoft-app-store-developer-responses-roll-out/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20871857/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/04/18/microsoft-app-store-developer-responses-roll-out/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应